column5: i love the trough of meat. i think health and hygiene would be an issue with buckets of ribs open in the middle of the floor and i think they will eat anything.
Funny cause its true, I'm pretty sure none of the photo were photoshopped.
If you want proof it's true, visit any Chinese grocery store in or around Toronto.
yup it's true.....  i often take my monster-in-law to the chinese grocery stores in town and i occasionally see the weirdest things
Almost reminds me of Honest Ed's, or the old St Lawrence and Kensington markets
People going through meat with their bare hands grossed me out the most. Is it really that bad??
